e Experience working with a non-profit, political or advocacy organization Experience with direct B2C customer support (or comparable experience) Advanced tech troubleshooting ability Excellent written English 9AM-5PM ET M-F schedule, with rotational on-call responsibilities on weekends for the final 5 weeks of the election cycle (Oct. 3 - November 1) Sense of humor, wit, and empathy for users Located in Washington D.C., Boston, New York Helpdesk software experience preferred (zendesk in particular) Interested? Please apply online now! 6uHXgII0F4 "
